  <brief_title>Positron Emission Tomography - Computed Tomography (PET-CT) Scan as a Diagnostic Method in Unknown Primary Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>PET-CT Scan as a Diagnostic Method in Unknown Primary Tumors</official_title>
